{"tid":1690242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗今日話唔好再提及721，即係7.21係狗狗死穴","createTime":"2019-11-03T08:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T14:48:14.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c24be9a42441071b8e937017d98e4f58fd936069","tid":1690242,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"網上有人發起下午在多個地區進行「行街」活動反對警暴，警方加強佈防。其中沙田大會堂百步梯有約100人聚集，多人被制服帶走。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者表示，下午約1時40分，數名男子在百步梯旁推撞，10多名市民圍觀，至少有3人被制服。<br />\n<br />\n數十名防暴警員隨即增援，進入大會堂公園再制服約5人，並帶上警車，並截查多名市民搜身。有在場警員表示，從被制服人士搜到鎚仔等工具，有警員就以粗言指罵身處平台聚集的市民，不滿有人向下投擲水樽。<br />\n<br />\n期間有市民一度與警員就執法問題理論，有警員向市民說「不要再提及7.21」，又警告該名市民不要再煽動其他人。另一名警察帶走同袍時說市民「壞咗個腦無得救」，市民起哄。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489808-20191103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489808-20191103.htm&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=68f8723a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489808-20191103.htm&h=b9ba91aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489808-20191103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a62388fb1dd21124cc096951da6166e122251e0e","tid":1690242,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"721 唔見人"},{"pid":"c85ee1e9d8e95616119f7405631e50c3f3859e39","tid":1690242,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"唔好再提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}